<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Do not drag me away with the wicked, those who do iniquity,</para>

<para style="q1">who speak peace with their neighbors but have evil in their hearts.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Give them what their deeds deserve and repay them what their wickedness demands,</para>

<para style="q1">repay them for the work of their hands and render to them their due.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />Because they do not understand the deeds of Yahweh or the work of his hands,</para>

<para style="q1">he will tear them down and never rebuild them.</para>

